      <title>贸易忧虑和股市暴跌导致泰铢涨势似乎减弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/baht-s-rally-looks-set-to-lose-steam-on-trade-angst-stock-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球贸易紧张局势升级以及泰国股市暴跌，今年泰铢的涨势似乎将逐渐减弱。]]></description>
