      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 22:26:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡零售交易员避开国内股票，转向热门的美国股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/singapore-retail-traders-shun-stocks-at-home-for-buzzy-us-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯尔文·陈 (Kelvin Tan) 于 2018 年开始进行网上投资，和许多新加坡人一样，他把所有的钱都投入了本地股票。两年后，他完全转向了美国股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/singapore-retail-traders-shun-stocks-at-home-for-buzzy-us-market</guid>
